fragments.plaintext:
Banks don't need to Hold Billions that's the point of ODL.

It settles in seconds so volatility wouldn't affect it as much to matter.

Volatility comes from buying and selling pressure not inate nature of the coin.

ODL  prevents/minimizes the affect of a "rug pull" by retail. 

Banks wouldn't need to Hold stock piles of XRP just enough for transaction fees the rest would be handled by ODL.

Ripple has many different financial products already.  Tokenization of RWA is just another product.
